name: Spurdo Spärde
description: It's a me, Spurdo! Spurdo Spärde (ticker: SPURDO) is a community-driven meme coin on the Solana blockchain, born on Pump.fun’s innovative fair‑launch platform. Combining the absurd charm of the Finnish “Spurdo” internet meme (a playful, poorly drawn Donald Duck parody) with on‑chain fellowship, SPURDO was launched without presales—ensuring equal token access from day one As part of Pump.fun’s ecosystem—a launchpad hosting millions of meme tokens—SPURDO embodies both humor and decentralization
